{"tid":1401203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（求前線勇武入黎）其實點解你地咁傾向留守？","createTime":"2019-08-03T14:24:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T15:53:59.000Z","uid":60231,"like":136,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"2e9432cedd0a9b1b8075f85240e2feafb5dc16cb","tid":1401203,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:24:37.000Z","msg":"由612起，每一次大街留守，我方都一定有人受傷/被捕<br />\n<br />\n唔駛講得好複雜，齋睇過去情況就知留守冇好處，係必輸，同埋你地既留守，只係不斷一見到蛋/畜龍就退後，威脅唔到d狗<br />\n<br />\n無論你投放幾多人力物力時間起防線，班狗都輕鬆拆（5分鐘左右就拆完）  畜龍輕鬆拉人打人<br />\n<br />\n相反，一見到防暴狗防線，就即刻四散，去第度重新聚集，咁就低成本高效益地撚狗<br />\n<br />\n所以我真心唔明你地留守黎做咩，根本傷唔到d狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇前線可以講解下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你地發夢嗰陣留守唔走係咪有咩特別既理由？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5066781321980ba499f04486fb34f1cf24a627","tid":1401203,"uid":241244,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:24:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化<br />\n明白大家唔同意見<br />\n呢篇野原意唔係反港獨<br />\n而係希望大家集中翻五大訴求</span></span><br />\n港獨？小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400357\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9b7ab040f04fccb82e7c1cda9282b9f39d74919e","tid":1401203,"uid":260005,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:25:13.000Z","msg":"我覺得有鬼"},{"pid":"8ca2f5a403fe90ecfbcb37132d8da353ae90012d","tid":1401203,"uid":19268,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:25:40.000Z","msg":"唔好賽後檢討住，集中推逃生post pls"},{"pid":"24fe85421f83d56fa30e363ad483e40d82bbf4e3","tid":1401203,"uid":274722,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T